result:
<!-- 编辑弹框 -->
    <a-modal
    title="编辑机器人命令集"
    style="top: 20px;"
    :width="600"
    v-model="visible"
    :destroyOnClose="true"
    @ok="handleSubmit"
  >
  <a-form :form="form">
    <a-form-item label="地图" :labelCol="labelCol" :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
      <a-select 
          placeholder="如需使用导航请先选择地图"
          optionFilterProp="children"
          v-decorator="['mapId']"
      >
        <a-select-option v-for="(item ,key) in mapList" :key="key" :value="item.id">
            {{item.mapName}}
          </a-select-option>
      </a-select>
    </a-form-item>
      <a-form-item
      label="命令集"
      :labelCol="labelCol"
      :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
      <a-select
          showSearch
          placeholder="选择命令集"
          optionFilterProp="children"
          :filterOption="filterOption"
          v-decorator="[
            'cmd',
            {rules: [{ required: true,message: '请选择' }],
            initialValue: editData.cmd}
          ]"
      >
          <a-select-option v-for="(item ,key) in cmdList" :key="key" :value="item.id">
            {{item.name}}
          </a-select-option>
      </a-select>
      <a-button type="primary" @click="$refs.cmd.show()">找不到合适的?点击配置命令集</a-button>
    </a-form-item>
  </a-form>
  
  <!-- <cmd-list ref="cmd"></cmd-list> -->
  </a-modal>
